-- 
EU Must Get Authority to Reform Economies, Volkskrant Reports

-- B y   F r e d   P a l s
-- 
2011-10-17T07:24:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/eu-must-get-authority-to-reform-economies-volkskrant-reports.html
The European Commission should get
the authority to force European Union states to reform their
economies if that is needed to solve economic problems and
prevent contagion, De Volkskrant reported today, citing a letter
in the newspaper from Maxime Verhagen, the Minister of Economic
Affairs.   The Dutch government will send a letter to parliament
explaining the proposal, the newspaper said without saying where
it obtained the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Fred Pals at 
 fpals@bloomberg.net  